{"tid":1287923,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"【文宣組請進】 紅白藍，一面代表香港人既旗幟","createTime":"2019-07-05T11:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T13:09:15.000Z","uid":5523,"like":8,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"95cb539a89e2eac72ad504029d58f5333dcdce1e","tid":1287923,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:51:17.000Z","msg":"我地一直無一支廣泛代表香港人既旗幟/圖案<br />\n但我認為代表香港既旗幟一早就係我地身邊<br />\n紅白藍, 代表<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">正義, 自由, 不忘初衷</span></span><br />\n每個香港人身邊, 都曾經有紅白藍, 紅白藍更加支撐住香港社會<br />\n就好似推車阿怕, 搬運阿叔, 義士物資站等等,<br />\n都有住紅白藍既蹤影<br />\n好多人有左財富, 權力之後, 就開始忘記過去支撐住自己既紅白藍,<br />\n但當香港人落難, 係香港人身邊, 香港人可以擁有, 同香港人共同進退既,<br />\n總可以搵到紅白藍<br />\n所以, 紅白藍就同正義, 自由, 一樣,<br />\n平時我地未必察覺佢既重要, 什至會被人遺忘, 比人睇唔起<br />\n但係今日, 香港人再一次走到絕路, 今次,<br />\n等我地高舉紅白藍, 紅白藍有好多種花式, 但唔重要<br />\n我地每個人都不同, 但我地同樣認同, 同樣追求正義, 自由<br />\n只要高舉紅白藍, 任何人都可以係追求正義, 自由既同路人!<br />\n紅白藍<br />\n你身邊總在有一個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f5/HK_Red-White-Blue_bags.JPG/800px-HK_Red-White-Blue_bags.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Ff%2Ff5%2FHK_Red-White-Blue_bags.JPG%2F800px-HK_Red-White-Blue_bags.JPG&h=92078a54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a0/Red-White-Blue.jpg/1280px-Red-White-Blue.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fa%2Fa0%2FRed-White-Blue.jpg%2F1280px-Red-White-Blue.jpg&h=5af8e7e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.vogue.com.tw/_rs/750/userfiles/thumbnail/sm1280_images_A0/2173/2011021759945345.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.vogue.com.tw%2F_rs%2F750%2Fuserfiles%2Fthumbnail%2Fsm1280_images_A0%2F2173%2F2011021759945345.jpg&h=2d5a1202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://rwb330.hk/media/007_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frwb330.hk%2Fmedia%2F007_2.jpg&h=ca6c82a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打點睇? 比D意見<br />\n覺我紅白藍3色代表既意義都好正面, 唔難搵<br />\n美國, 法國都有用紅白藍<br />\n大家唔難聯想到自由, 平等, 博愛<br />\n同埋勇氣, 真理, 正義<br />\n而且香港人都可以接受, 係最容易入屋<br />\n下面可以討論, 正式既紅白藍旗幟可以點樣組成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e31b9a4b9b1532a8f9aac8829127ff7bf91fba3","tid":1287923,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:51:59.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5e8ba05fc2d751ddf931b65388860a5047543f","tid":1287923,"uid":1797,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:52:21.000Z","msg":"先唔講新旗好唔好<br />\n唔想再見到紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3bcecc90f07a55b401aabb4c3034ab43e07b77d","tid":1287923,"uid":5523,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ed5e8ba05fc2d751ddf931b65388860a5047543f","tid":1287923,"uid":1797,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:52:21.000Z","msg":"先唔講新旗好唔好<br />\n唔想再見到紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:56:37.000Z","msg":"全紅就共產, 鮮血, 革命, 鬥爭<br />\n但紅白藍加埋就唔係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4784bcd6733e681c9c248a22454ba560d7c168","tid":1287923,"uid":165336,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:57:08.000Z","msg":"紅白藍唸起法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a7753cef93a14fe39b10541fa5dbf4bb1f06aa","tid":1287923,"uid":198503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db4784bcd6733e681c9c248a22454ba560d7c168","tid":1287923,"uid":165336,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:57:08.000Z","msg":"紅白藍唸起法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:57:41.000Z","msg":"點唸？<br />\n<br />\n諗就得"},{"pid":"d67a974ee2ddc3e77f0d4aeb586a311e084fe69b","tid":1287923,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"db4784bcd6733e681c9c248a22454ba560d7c168","tid":1287923,"uid":165336,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:57:08.000Z","msg":"紅白藍唸起法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:59:29.000Z","msg":"4隻紅白藍花加埋, 左上, 右上, 左下, 右下<br />\n做正式紅白藍旗既初形<br />\n有無得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c8edcdb46c47df8cdf826c7d68e988ffe0b87d","tid":1287923,"uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:00:06.000Z","msg":"藍色部份多啲會較好"},{"pid":"35af222bf59732509a0a6d431962ae87bbcc0ee2","tid":1287923,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:04:13.000Z","msg":"唔要紅！仲赤唔夠呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0db395d0dbd2bda88350ed1bef6ff559598df3","tid":1287923,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"35af222bf59732509a0a6d431962ae87bbcc0ee2","tid":1287923,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:04:13.000Z","msg":"唔要紅！仲赤唔夠呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KrrZxYL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKrrZxYL.jpg&h=96aace23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n定D黎..<br />\n用呢隻紅, 唔用共產血紅<br />\n好唔好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"666937480df56ebeab89febcbed89617e22eda03","tid":1287923,"uid":250036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:10:19.000Z","msg":"一定要有Hong Kong is not China 嗰隻藍色"},{"pid":"2cd3139ac3f3b408a7078ce834b558a85f0a74a8","tid":1287923,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"